commit.message: Created a python function (FoodFacts.py) to get a nutrition fact based on product name.
Created a function to return the url of the top match of the data (findProductUrl.py).  This works with ExtractingNutrition.py.
A start to find the url given a product name.
Made the program into a function that takes in a url and a key (such as Calories).
Created a python program to make a dictionary out of a specific url.
